log: Heartkit has drawn the ire of Pinnaclerain by deliberately taking the last of their favorite nesting materials for themselves. (medium negative effect)
Heartkit had Whistleshock surprise them with something nice. (medium positive effect)
Heartkit thinks they can tell Minnie something important. (high positive effect)
Heartpaw had a disagreement with Kitepelt while on patrol earlier. (medium negative effect)
Heartpaw had a fight with Crouchpaw. (high negative effect)
Heartkit mews congratulations to Bluekit for a job well done. (low positive effect)
Heartpaw gives Alpinepaw a wonderfully colored pebble they found, and hides behind their whiskers when thanked. (high positive effect)
Heartpaw bickered about something trivial with Windpaw. (neutral effect)
Heartpaw is sharing prey with Dreampaw. (medium positive effect)
Heartkit plays mossball with Pigeonkit. (medium positive effect)
